channel.title: My server wont go online please help!
channel.description: ok so i posted my server on runelocus its called klownscape than i go into my source folder click run and than it tells me the servers online so i goto my no-ip DUC that i downloaded off of a guide and its working fine so i goto runelocus and refresh the page and it says my servers online at 50% , ok cool but i turn my computer off to goto bed than the next day i do all the same stuff and it says my servers offline and it wont go back online but i can play it fine its just runelocus keeps saying its offline so does anyone know how to change this? it would be a great help... thanks.
